# =============================================================================
#  NCI — Financial Market Dependence Network
#  S&P 500 Top-20 Large-Cap Stocks, 2015–2025
#  Daily returns from Yahoo Finance (via quantmod)
#
#  Riso & Zoia (2026) — Empirical Application: Equity Dependence Networks
#
#  Nodes  = 20 S&P 500 stocks by market cap
#  Edges  = Minimum Spanning Tree of the return correlation matrix
#  Weights = w_i = MarketCap_i / Σ MarketCap_j
#  Indices = Baseline NCI  vs  HHI  vs  Gini
# =============================================================================

